<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>エンゼルキング 在庫管理</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif; background: #f5f4f2; }

  header {
    background: #2c2c2c; color: #fff;
    padding: 14px 16px 10px;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  header h1 { font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  header p  { font-size: 10px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 2px; }

  .stats {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat {
    background: #3a3a3a; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 5px 12px; text-align: center; flex: 1; min-width: 60px;
  }
  .stat .num { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat .lbl { font-size: 9px; color: #aaa; }

  .controls {
    background: #fff; padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;
  }
  .controls input[type=text] {
    border: 1.5px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 14px; flex: 1; min-width: 140px; outline: none;
  }
  .controls input[type=text]:focus { border-color: #888; }

  .filter-row {
    background: #fff; padding: 8px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .filter-btn {
    padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1.5px solid #ddd;
    background: #fff; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .filter-btn.active { background: #2c2c2c; color: #fff; border-color: #2c2c2c; }

  .page-tabs {
    background: #fff; padding: 8px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .page-tab {
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid #ddd;
    background: #fff; font-size: 11px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.15s; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .page-tab.active { background: #2c2c2c; color: #fff; border-color: #2c2c2c; }

  .sort-row {
    background: #faf9f7; padding: 6px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888;
  }
  .sort-btn {
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;
    background: #fff; font-size: 11px; cursor: pointer;
  }
  .sort-btn.active { background: #2c2c2c; color: #fff; border-color: #2c2c2c; }

  .legend {
    padding: 6px 14px; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 11px; color: #888; background: #faf9f7;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }
  .legend span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
  .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block; }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  th {
    background: #f0ede8; padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #666;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e0ddd9; text-align: left; position: sticky; top: 0;
  }
  td { padding: 6px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ede8; font-size: 13px; }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #faf9f7; }

  .color-num { font-family: monospace; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
  .col-num   { font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; }

  .status-btn {
    width: 52px; height: 28px; border-radius: 6px; border: none;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.1s;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }
  .status-btn:active { transform: scale(0.9); }
  .s-cross  { background: #f1f0ee; color: #999; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; }
  .s-1      { background: #ffe8cc; color: #a05f00; border: 1.5px solid #f5c97f; }
  .s-2      { background: #ffe8cc; color: #a05f00; border: 1.5px solid #f5c97f; }
  .s-3      { background: #d4edda; color: #2d6a4f; border: 1.5px solid #7dd3b0; }
  .s-4      { background: #d4edda; color: #2d6a4f; border: 1.5px solid #7dd3b0; }
  .s-5      { background: #d4edda; color: #2d6a4f; border: 1.5px solid #7dd3b0; }
  .s-5plus  { background: #ffcccc; color: #c0392b; border: 1.5px solid #f5a97f; }

  .updated { font-size: 10px; color: #bbb; }

  .empty { padding: 40px; text-align: center; color: #bbb; font-size: 14px; }

  .save-banner {
    background: #e8f4e8; border-bottom: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
    padding: 5px 14px; font-size: 11px; color: #2e7d32;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .save-banner span { color: #888; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>ANGELKING ミシン刺繍糸 在庫管理</h1>
  <p>タップして在庫を切り替え　× → 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 → 5 → 5本以上 → ×</p>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="cnt-total" style="color:#fff">-</div><div class="lbl">表示</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="cnt-rich" style="color:#ffaaaa">-</div><div class="lbl">5本以上</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="cnt-ok" style="color:#7dd3b0">-</div><div class="lbl">在庫あり</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="cnt-low" style="color:#f5c97f">-</div><div class="lbl">残りわずか</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="cnt-zero" style="color:#f5a97f">-</div><div class="lbl">在庫なし</div></div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="save-banner">
  💾 変更は自動保存されます（このブラウザ内）
  <span id="save-status">保存済</span>
</div>

<div class="controls">
  <input type="text" id="search" placeholder="色番号で検索..." oninput="render()">
</div>

<div class="filter-row" id="filter-row"></div>
<div class="page-tabs" id="page-tabs"></div>

<div class="sort-row">
  並び替え：
  <button class="sort-btn active" onclick="setSort('default',this)">糸帳順</button>
  <button class="sort-btn" onclick="setSort('asc',this)">番号昇順</button>
  <button class="sort-btn" onclick="setSort('desc',this)">番号降順</button>
  <button class="sort-btn" onclick="setSort('status',this)">在庫順</button>
</div>

<div class="legend">
  <span><span class="dot" style="background:#ffcccc;border:1px solid #f5a97f"></span>5本以上</span>
  <span><span class="dot" style="background:#d4edda;border:1px solid #7dd3b0"></span>3〜5本</span>
  <span><span class="dot" style="background:#ffe8cc;border:1px solid #f5c97f"></span>1〜2本</span>
  <span><span class="dot" style="background:#f1f0ee;border:1px solid #ccc"></span>在庫なし</span>
</div>

<div id="table-wrap">
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>色番号</th><th>列</th><th>在庫</th><th>更新日</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody id="tbody"></tbody>
  </table>
</div>

